      "title": "Children and prejudice",
      "abstract": "What is prejudice and ethnic awareness? theories of prejudice the development of ethnic attitudes and prejudice the development of ethnic awareness and identification critical examination of design and measures social and psychological determinants of prejudice social-cognitive developments related to prejudice a note to educators."
